### Getting Started

- Install dev hooks:

```bash
pre-commit install --install-hooks
```

- Run quality gates:

```bash
make format && make lint && make type && make test && make docs
```

- Configure env via [settings.py](mdc:src/ultimate_discord_intelligence_bot/settings.py) and [docs/configuration.md](mdc:docs/configuration.md)

